thread.title: Marika Runfors
thread.title_full: Redspot Car Rentals reviewed by Marika Runfors

author: Marika Runfors
title: Marika Runfors
text: Hired a car for 10 days and everything worked out beautifully. Got our bonds back, didnt have to fight about insurance and they cleaned up the car after you when you gave it back. Superfriendly staff and the car was in excellent condition. Would definitely rent from them again
